headline: Pulnovo Medical Names Dr. Francis Duhay as Global Chief Medical Officer
summary: Pulnovo Medical, a global leader in mechanism-driven therapies for Pulmonary Hypertension (PH) and Heart Failure (HF), today announced the appointment of Francis Duhay, MD, MBA, FACS as Global Chief Medical Officer.
